# Effect Source Code Reference

A local copy of the Effect source is available at `ts/vendor/effect/`.

When writing or modifying CLI code that uses Effect APIs, consult:
- `ts/vendor/effect/packages/cli/src/` for @effect/cli patterns (Command, Options, Args)
- `ts/vendor/effect/packages/effect/src/` for core Effect patterns (Effect.gen, Layer, Service)
- `ts/vendor/effect/packages/platform/src/` for @effect/platform patterns (FileSystem, Terminal)

Key patterns used in this CLI:
- Commands defined with `Command.make().pipe(Command.withHandler(...))`
- Options defined with `Options.text()`, `Options.boolean()`, etc.
- Services as `Effect.Service<T>()` classes with Layer composition
- Error handling with tagged errors and `Effect.gen(function* () { ... })`
